'''Proclamation Boards''' were large holographic viewscreens installed in the [[Grand Concourse]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. They were designed to keep [[Senator/Legends|senators]] informed of the war's progress and display [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine's]] executive decrees.

==Appearances==
*[[Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith (novelization)|''Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith'' novelization]] {{Ab|Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith (unabridged audiobook)}}

